107998, "trip_id": 9405429, "location_id": 103758014, "main_media_item_path": null, "name": null, "display_name": "Oppdal", "description": "Treintje van 10u tot 12, aangekomen in kongsvoll. Let the adventure begin", "slug": "oppdal", "display_slug": "oppdal", "type": 1, "start_time": 1698836533.436, "end_time": null, "creation_time": 1698931536.211, "location": {"id": 103758014, "name": "Oppdal", "detail": "Norway", "full_detail": "Norway", "country_code": "NO", "lat": 62.3068801, "lon": 9.6063484, "admin_area_code": null, "uuid": "246a5886-5eb7-44b2-99d0-03d2b34ab0e8"}, "supertype": "normal", "is_deleted": false, "open_graph_id": null, "fb_publish_status": null, "timezone_id": "Europe/Oslo", "views": 0, "comment_count": 0, "weather_condition": "snow", "weather_temperature": -8, "uuid": "693d0a6c-b6bc-4d65-8cab-aed68268d6ed"}, {"id": 83107898, "trip_id": 9405429, "location_id": 103757901, "main_media_item_path": null, "name": null, "display_name": "Oppdal", "description": "Oepsie 12 miles ipv km ...\n\nWordt nipt om voor het donker aan te komen, zijn om 12u vertrokken en moeten 19km \n\nWel de muskusos 3/4 keer gezien, zelfs baby's !", "slug": "oppdal", "display_slug": "oppdal", "type": 1, "start_time": 1698844469.007, "end_time": null, "creation_time": 1698931383.009, "location": {"id": 103757901, "name": "Oppdal", "detail": "Norway", "full_detail": "Norway", "country_code": "NO", "lat": 62.306480845436454, "lon": 9.527251180261374, "admin_area_code": null, "uuid": "36609831-bc66-43e9-bd6a-4f7c95b39f14"}, "supertype": "normal", "is_deleted": false, "open_graph_id": null, "fb_publish_status": null, "timezone_id": "Europe/Oslo", "views": 0, "comment_count": 0, "weather_condition": "snow", "weather_temperature": -9, "uuid": "e7edfe53-99eb-4104-bfb2-dacbd67d732d"}, {"id": 83109114, "trip_id": 9405429, "location_id": 103759328, "main_media_item_path": null, "name": null, "display_name": "Oppdal", "description": "Aangekomen om 18:30 bij -16\u00b0\ud83d\udc80\n\nAlle gsm's plat behalve die van Wannes, geen bereik voor de laatste 5 kilometer en zakken door de diepsneeuw bezorgt ons wat problemen.\nWe hebben ook nog een halfuur in t donker moeten wandelen en paar stresskes gehad omdat we de cabine pas heel laat zagen.\n\nBut all gooddd\nLekker pasta gekookt, de cabine zelf had ook heel veel eten. En we hebben onze spullen opgewarmd, maar mijn schoenen gesmolten oeps.\n\nSochtends 6u opgestaan om vroeg te vertrekken (7:30u ong), we doen een korter route (16km) maar moeten de trein om 13:30 halen!!", "slug": "oppdal", "display_slug": "oppdal", "type": 1, "start_time": 1698907564.158, "end_time": null, "creation_time": 1698932289.543, "location": {"id": 103759328, "name": "Oppdal", "detail": "Norway", "full_detail": "Norway", "country_code": "NO", "lat": 62.3412979, "lon": 9.3562764, "admin_area_code": null, "uuid": "c5085031-80b1-4eaa-abf2-ad619b3e7163"}, "supertype": "normal", "is_deleted": false, "open_graph_id": null, "fb_publish_status": null, "timezone_id": "Europe/Oslo", "views": 0, "comment_count": 0, "weather_condition": "snow", "weather_temperature": -6, "uuid": "b9213f40-b877-48af-a8c5-ae6576766381"}, {"id": 83109203, "trip_id": 9405429, "location_id": 103759422, "main_media_item_path": null, "name": null, "display_name": "Oppdal", "description": "Ah fuck deze trail leidt niet naar het station, hebben nog maar 1.15u en moeten nog offroad overkruisen door de diepsneeuw naar het pad van gisteren en dan nog 4km dat pad volgen.\n\nHet totale km aantal is dus wrs nog meer dan gisteren eigenlijk (20km?) en we hebben minder dan 6u gerekend om het te doen...\n\nGa ni halen", "slug": "oppdal", "display_slug": "oppdal", "type": 1, "start_time": 1698923712.662, "end_time": null, "creation_time": 1698932561.751, "location": {"id": 103759422, "name": "Oppdal", "detail": "Norway", "full_detail": "Norway", "country_code": "NO", "lat": 62.3028478, "lon": 9.5326179, "admin_area_code": null, "uuid": "c6b95501-77ab-48e8-ba98-d171e6fc4b05"}, "supertype": "normal", "is_deleted": false, "open_graph_id": null, "fb_publish_status": null, "timezone_id": "Europe/Oslo", "views": 0, "comment_count": 0, "weather_condition": "snow", "weather_temperature": -5, "uuid": "61520041-170f-473d-a4f9-6410b75f127b"}, {"id": 83109710, "trip_id": 9405429, "location_id": 103759998, "main_media_item_path": null, "name": null, "display_name": "Oppdal", "description": "Holy shit, laatste 4km echt gespeedrunned. De cross was heel kut maar het pad daarna chill.\nVooral de laatste 1.5km door het bos grotendeels gelopen (en op ons bek gaan oeps). Dan met onze laatste energie over de snelweg 10 min gelopen en om 13:29 aangekomen!!!", "slug": "oppdal", "display_slug": "oppdal", "type": 1, "start_time": 1698927996.704, "end_time": null, "creation_time": 1698932629.702, "location": {"id": 103759998, "name": "Oppdal", "detail": "Norway", "full_detail": "Norway", "country_code": "NO", "lat": 62.3041748, "lon": 9.6055171, "admin_area_code": null, "uuid": "c6223742-9604-457c-8e1f-911d2f2ab56b"}, "supertype": "normal", "is_deleted": false, "open_graph_id": null, "fb_publish_status": null, "timezone_id": "Europe/Oslo", "views": 0, "comment_count": 0, "weather_condition": "snow", "weather_temperature": -5, "uuid": "83d78849-8874-4842-ab4e-e2eebe05319b"}]}